  "text": [
    "Taking root in windy sand",
    "is not an easy",
    "way",
    "to go about",
    "finding a place to stay.",
    "A ditchbank or wood's-edge",
    "has firmer ground.",
    "In a loose world though",
    "something can be started\u2014",
    "a root touch water,",
    "a tip break sand\u2014",
    "Mounds from that can rise",
    "on held mounds,",
    "a gesture of building, keeping,",
    "a trapping",
    "into shape.",
    "Firm ground is not available ground."
  ],
  "title": "Dunes",
  "year": ""
